OL,3,CEvangelical priest faces charges of
OL,4,Csexually assaulting followers
OL,6,FA priest who led an evangelical
OL,7,Fmovement in the 1980s and 1990s has
OL,8,Fappeared in court to face multiple
OL,9,Fallegations of sexual offences against
OL,10,Fformer members of a church
OL,11,Fcongregation.
OL,13,FThe Reverend Christopher Brain led the
OL,14,Fso-called Nine O'Clock Service in
OL,15,Fbetween 1986 and 1995.
OL,17,FBrain appeared at Sheffield
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court for a four-minute
OL,19,Fhearing on Monday, where he faced a
OL,20,Ftotal of 34 charges in relation to 11
OL,21,Fwomen.
