OL,3,CEvangelical priest faces charges of
OL,4,Csexually assaulting followers
OL,6,FHe is accused of sexual offences
OL,7,Fagainst women who had joined the
OL,8,Fmovement, police have said.
OL,10,FBrain, now 66, of Park Road, Wilmslow,
OL,11,FCheshire, is charged with one count of
OL,12,Frape and 33 counts of indecent
OL,13,Fassault, alleged to have been
OL,14,Fcommitted between 1981 and 1995.
OL,16,FHe stood in the glass-fronted dock for
OL,17,Fthe short hearing, wearing a grey suit
OL,18,Fand black open-necked shirt.
OL,20,FHe spoke to give his name, date of
OL,21,Fbirth and address.
