OL,6,FDistrict Judge Marcus Waite granted
OL,7,Fhim unconditional bail and told him to
OL,8,Fappear again at Sheffield Crown Court
OL,9,Fon April 15.
OL,11,FOnly the charge of rape was read out
OL,12,Fin full in court on Monday.
OL,14,FThe judge told Brain the allegation
OL,15,Fwas so serious it needed to be dealt
OL,16,Fwith by a crown court judge and that
OL,17,Fthe other 33 counts would also be
OL,18,Ftransferred.
