OL,4,Csexually assaulting followers
OL,6,FThe 33 indecent assault charges
OL,7,Finclude some which cover multiple
OL,8,Fdifferent alleged incidents, including
OL,9,Fa number involving allegations of
OL,10,Fassault during massages.
OL,12,FBrain left the court building with his
OL,13,Fsolicitor, wearing a surgical mask.
OL,15,FThe Nine O'Clock Service was initially
OL,16,Fheld at St Thomas's Church, in the
OL,17,FCrookes area of Sheffield, before
OL,18,Fmoving to Ponds Forge sport complex in
OL,19,Fthe city centre.
